  "body": "<h1><p><a href=\"https://www.patreon.com/quillphen\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\"> <img src=\"https://img.shields.io/badge/Support me-Patreon-ff424d?logo=patreon&amp;logoColor=white\" alt=\"Support me on Patreon\"></a> &nbsp;&nbsp;<a href=\"https://discord.gg/8GydmUN3xq\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\"><img src=\"https://img.shields.io/badge/Join our Discord-5865F2?logo=discord&amp;logoColor=white\" alt=\"Join our Discord\"> </a>\n  &nbsp;&nbsp;  <a href=\"https://ko-fi.com/quillphen\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\"><img src=\"https://img.shields.io/badge/Support me-Ko--fi-571db5?logo=kofi&logoColor=white\" alt=\"Support me on Ko-fi\"></a></h1>\n\n<p align=\"center\">\n  <a href=\"https://www.patreon.com/cw/quillphen\" target=\"_blank\">\n    <img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/49b1e899a9f41e7eeeb877bc53e8d5838998a95b_0.webp\" alt=\"Patreon\">\n  </a>\n</p>\n  \n    \n# Dynamic Light Shader\n> A simple baseline shader that glows/emits light from held items in your hand.\nLight color based on the item you are holding (torch, lantern, glowstone, redstone, soul items, etc.).\n\n> ![dynamic lights](https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/fw4J9UkQ/images/33fcd3edfa2552311a2e52db0a133498050d28d2.gif)\n\nYou can **disable(0)/enable(1)** the held_color_light from shader pack settings\n\n\nthats it!\ncontributions are welcome (https://github.com/Hiba550/Dynamic-Light-Shader)",
